\par }\pard \s17\qj\ri40\sl288\slmult1\nowidctlpar {\fs26 Chu\'c8n dung t\'ddch b\'bbng thu\'fb tinh \'ae\'ad\'eec ki\'d3m \'ae\'denh theo ph\'ad\'acng ph\'b8p c\'a9n. Th\'d3 t\'ddch ch\'cat l\'e1ng \'f8ng v\'edi m\'f8c dung t\'ddch c\'c7n ki\'d3m tra c\'f1
a chu\'c8n \'ae\'ad\'eec x\'b8c \'ae\'denh qua kh\'e8i l\'ad\'eeng v\'b5 kh\'e8i l\'ad\'eeng ri\'aang c\'f1a n\'e3, c\'e3 t\'ddnh \'ae\'d5n s\'e8 hi\'d6u ch\'d8nh do s\'f8c \'ae\'c8y c\'f1a kh\'abng kh\'dd. 
\par }\pard\plain \nowidctlpar \f15\fs28 {\fs26 
